OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FHeavy rain clearing northeast
OL,6,Fcoasts in the early morning. The rest
OL,7,Fof the day will be cloudy at times but
OL,8,Fwith bright or sunny spells and
OL,9,Fscattered showers, these heavy at
OL,10,Ftimes, especially in the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers mostly dying out this
OL,13,Fevening with late bright or sunny
OL,14,Fspells. Overnight will be dry with
OL,15,Fclear spells before cloud and patchy
OL,16,Frain spreads into the south around
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
