OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FMostly cloudy with some
OL,6,Fbrighter spells towards northern
OL,7,Fcoasts in the morning. Dry for most in
OL,8,Fthe morning but light and patchy rain
OL,9,Fspreading northwards in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,12,For sunny spells and some heavy showers
OL,13,FTuesday. Bright spells and showers at
OL,14,Ffirst Wednesday, heavy rain later.
OL,15,FMostly cloudy with heavy showers on
OL,16,FThursday. Breezy Wednesday and
OL,17,FThursday.
